    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic order. This specimen features the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver a linear 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for superior power distribution. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with documented tolerances. The suspension geometry remains tight, and the cross-drilled rotors provide firm, fade-free deceleration. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
